        Product description

        First Partner:
        You are going on your adventure with one of the three pupper-type "Meowa", a "Hogata", and a "weezer".
        How do I encounter and tell story?

        Legendary Pokemon "Mirainon"
        It is said to have the power to far outperform other Pokemon, but its ecology is shrouded in mystery.
        Riding on the back of "Miraint" allows you to run on land, swim, glide and climb cliffs for even more adventure.

        (Terrastal)
        The phenomenon of the Paldea region allows all Pokémon live in this region to "Terrastal". Each Pokémon has a "terra type" and can be changed to "terrestal".
        Most Pokémon have the same "terra type" as their original types, but some of them seem to have different types from their original types. In the Pokémon battles in the Paldeaa region, the "Terrastal" will hold the key to the game.

        Connects via communication:
        This product can be multiplayed for up to 4 players at the same time. In addition to playing communications such as Pokémon exchanges, competitions, and you can also explore the same field as other players.
        You can also play with other players in the "Terraide Battle" where you can encounter terrestal Pokemon in the wild.

        How are ratings calculated?
        To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzes reviews to verify trustworthiness.
